verbose_text: In addition, recent evidence shows that the Sry gene on the Y chromosome is only expressed in TH containing neurons in the substantia nigra (SN) and can activate TH production in SN neurons that project to the striatum independently of gonadal hormones.
evidence: Sry gene on the Y chromosome is only expressed in TH-containing neurons in the substantia nigra (SN) and can activate TH production in SN
